n: Cranberry Orange Relish with Orange Flavored Liqueur
des: "This is an easy and delicious cranberry orange relish. Much of its sweet orange flavor comes from the liqueur, however it can be omitted."
ins:
In a food processor, grinder, or blender, combine the cranberries, orange and sugar. Blend until evenly chopped.
Stir in the liqueur and refrigerate for several hours to allow flavors to blend.
